name: Flo and Boo
description:
Scrapling Doll called Flo
Handcrafted from scraps of material , doll is made from calico
Hand sewn and felted  face details 
Filled with safety standard toy stuffing
Measures 21" high
Cream wool hair ,rose printed cotton dress and a pink scarf
Intended as a collectors item not suitable for children under 14 years old 
Can be sponged clean if it gets grubby

name: Girly Gertrude and Spike
description:
Girly Scrapling doll
Handcrafted from scraps of material , doll is made from calico and striped cotton
She carries a bag with her little friend Spike in it
Hand painted face details 
Filled with safety standard toy stuffing
Measures 21" high
Black wool hair , gingham bow and leg warmers
Intended as a collectors item not suitable for children under 14 years old

name: Milly and Mooby
description:
This is a new Scrapling doll named Milly with her pet mouse Mooby

She stands 22" tall and is filled with safety standard toy stuffing

She is dressed in pretty blue clothes and sports a dashing bow around her neck the mouse brooch is removable

She  is not suitable for under 14 years old is better used as a feature sitting on a sofa or a shelf.

Shecan be spot cleaned

name: Morris
description:
Morris is a classy dresser in his striped suit and bow tie , he loves travelling 

He stands 18" tall and is filled with safety standard toy stuffing

He sports a red striped suit and a black tie

He is not suitable for under 14 years old is better used as a feature sitting on a sofa or a shelf.

He can be spot cleaned if he gets grubby

name: Mr Candyman
description:
This is a new Scrapling doll named Mr Candyman

He stands 22" tall and is filled with safety standard toy stuffing

He sports a nifty black hat , his suit is embroidered maroon silk 

He is not suitable for under 14 years old is better used as a feature sitting on a sofa or a shelf.

He is very partial to candy hence his name so make sure that he does not raid the sweetie jar

He can be spot cleaned
